title: Mara
text:
I’m the oldest of five children.
I taught English to first graders in China.
I’m a circus artist who specializes in hand balancing! (aka, balancing on my hands)
I’m an MPS in Natural Resources, and I’m interested in adaptive land management practices that protect and enhance biodiversity.
